================================================================================

= EXAMPLE OF SUGGESTED DIRECTORY STRUCTURE FOR DEVELOPMENT =

/                                   <--- ROOT and PUBLIC_ROOT
    apps/                           <--- APPS_ROOT
        ...
    data/                           <--- DATA_ROOT
        ...
    docs/
        ...
    logicoder/                      <--- LOGICODER_ROOT
        libraries/
        helpers/
        ...
    media/                          <--- MEDIA_ROOT
        ...
    tests/
        ...
    .htaccess
    index.php
    settings.php

================================================================================

= EXAMPLE OF RECOMMENDED DIRECTORY STRUCTURE FOR LIVE DEPLOYMENT =

/                                   <--- ROOT (usually a /home/* folder)
    apps/                           <--- APPS_ROOT
        common/
        default/
            /controllers/
            /models/
            /views/
            /libraries/
            /i18n/
                /en/
                /es/
                /it/
        ...
    data/                           <--- DATA_ROOT (write access needed)
        cache/
        logs/
        upload/
        ...
    logicoder/                      <--- LOGICODER_ROOT
        libraries/
        helpers/
        ...
    public_html/                    <--- PUBLIC_ROOT
        .htaccess
        index.php
        settings.php
        media/                      <--- MEDIA_ROOT
            css/
            download/
            images/
            js/
            photos/
            swf/
            thumbs/
            videos/
            ...
